N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 661.12 - Sequence of accounts

State Regulations

The order in which the accounts are presented in this
system of accounts is not to be considered as necessarily indicative of the
order in which they will be scheduled at all times in reports to this
commission. Notes
